    <section aria-labelledby="about-story">
      <h2 id="about-story">Our Story</h2>
      <p>
        Four Winds Roots Pharmacy is an independent community pharmacy in Centennial Plaza
        at 3932A Keele Street, North York — at the intersection of Keele Street and Finch
        Avenue West, in the heart of the York University Heights neighbourhood.
      </p>
      <p>
        Unlike chain pharmacies, Four Winds Roots operates as a
        <strong>registered holistic pharmacy</strong>, taking the time to understand your
        full health picture — not just the prescription in front of you. That means reviewing
        your medications alongside your herbs, supplements, and wellness goals.
      </p>
