    <section aria-labelledby="about-pharmacist">
      <h2 id="about-pharmacist">Meet Your Pharmacist</h2>
      <!-- TODO: add photo of Winston Clarke with alt text; add OCP registration number once confirmed -->
      <p>
        <strong>Winston Clarke</strong> is the pharmacist at Four Winds Roots Pharmacy.
        Winston brings a whole-person approach to pharmacy practice — taking the time to
        talk through your medications, understand your health goals, and flag any interactions
        between your prescriptions and the supplements or herbs you take.
      </p>
      <p>
