    <section aria-labelledby="about-wellness">
      <h2 id="about-wellness">Meet Our Wellness Practitioner</h2>
      <!-- TODO: add photo of Pamela Clarke with alt text -->
      <!--
        COMPLIANCE NOTE: "Natural Health Practitioner" is NOT a regulated title under Ontario's
        Regulated Health Professions Act. Pamela Clarke must be described exactly as her directory
        listing states — do not use "RN", "Registered Nurse", or list private credentials.
        Her private-accreditation affiliations are not regulated and must not be cited as
        professional qualifications in marketing copy.
      -->
      <p>
        <strong>Pamela Clarke</strong> is our Natural Health Practitioner and wellness author.
        Pamela focuses on the intersection of natural health and conventional medicine —
        helping patients understand how herbs, supplements, and whole-person wellness
        practices fit alongside their pharmacy care.
      </p>
      <p>
        Pamela is the author of <em>Take Control Now: Your Health Is Your Responsibility</em>
        (FriesenPress, 2015) — a guide to taking an active role in your own health.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="/holistic-wellness">Learn about our holistic wellness approach &rarr;</a>
      </p>
    </section>

    <section aria-labelledby="about-holistic">
      <h2 id="about-holistic">A Different Kind of Pharmacy</h2>
      <p>
        Four Winds Roots is a registered holistic pharmacy that deals with herbs and drug
        interactions — meaning we look at everything you put in your body, not just what's
        on your prescription label. Whether you take herbal remedies, vitamins, or specialty
        supplements alongside your medications, we review the full picture for safety.
      </p>
      <p>
        And because optical care and wellness services are available alongside our dispensary,
        you can take care of more of your health in one visit.
      </p>
